OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772041214
OL,3,CPeter Mandelson complains to
OL,4,Cjournalists about news coverage of his
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FLord Peter Mandelson has been
OL,8,Fmessaging journalists to complain
OL,9,Fabout news coverage of his arrest on
OL,10,FMonday.
OL,12,FThe former Labour spin doctor was also
OL,13,Fsaid to have been texting friends in
OL,14,Fthe early hours of Tuesday,
OL,15,Fcriticising the police for arresting
OL,16,Fhim.
OL,18,FThe 72-year-old was held by police for
OL,19,Fnine hours of questioning following
OL,20,Fhis arrest on suspicion of misconduct
OL,21,Fin public office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
