PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772041214
OL,3,CPeter Mandelson complains to
OL,4,Cjournalists about news coverage of his
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,F"There is absolutely no truth
OL,8,Fwhatsoever in any such suggestion. We
OL,9,Fhave asked the MPS for the evidence
OL,10,Frelied upon to justify the arrest.
OL,12,F"Peter Mandelson's overriding priority
OL,13,Fis to cooperate with the police
OL,14,Finvestigation, as he has done
OL,15,Fthroughout this process, and to clear
OL,16,Fhis name."
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
